description: The skill was built to provide Amazon Echo users with jokes that they might have heard of but haven't heard or have forgotten. As an added bonus I've included jokes of my own. Enjoy!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Jokes Galore tell me a joke
Alexa, ask Jokes Galore say a joke
name: Jokes Galore
shortDescription: Funny puns and jokes for any one looking for a chuckle.
